<materialsCitation id="0FAA3CAEFFAC1B1BFE32F6EF03144FDD" ID-GBIF-Occurrence="3336142330" pageId="18" pageNumber="168">Agana, April 16, 19, May 4, at light, Bryan; Piti, May 30, June 8, 12, July 12, at light, Swezey; Piti, May 9, at light, Usinger. Grubs were found at corn roots at Dededo, Nov. 25, Swezey.</materialsCitation>
</paragraph>
